              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>What started as a simple conversation between two friends turned into a bigger vision. We kept asking ourselves one question: <em>why do people prefer specialty coffee over regular instant coffee?</em></p><p>The answer was clear — it’s all about the experience. The aroma, the freshness, the precision, and most importantly, the taste.</p><p>That’s where we come in.</p><p>Our mission is simple: <strong>to make specialty coffee accessible to everyone</strong> — not just cafés or experts, but anyone who enjoys a great cup of coffee. We believe you shouldn’t have to compromise on quality because of price.</p><p>We offer a carefully selected range of:</p><ul><li>Coffee machines<br/></li><li>Brewing tools<br/></li><li>Coffee equipment<br/></li><li>Accessories for both beginners and professionals<br/></li></ul><p>Whether you’re just starting your coffee journey or you’re already passionate about brewing, we aim to provide everything you need — at some of the most competitive rates in the market.</p><p>We’re not just selling products. We’re helping you create better coffee moments, every day.</p><p>Because at the end of the day, great coffee shouldn’t be a luxury — it should be a standard.</p>",
